node.text:
🚨 GOV BALL GIVEAWAY 🚨 THIS JUST IN: @omgheyrose is back and she’s got some HOT GOSS. BABE 100 is announcing 100 MORE HOURS OF SUMMER! To celebrate this groundbreaking news, BABE 100 is giving away the ULTIMATE VIP @GOVBALLNYC GETAWAY. You and your bestie could win:

☀️ 2 VIP @GOVBALLNYC WEEKEND PASSES
☀️ 100 HOURS IN A FANCY-ASS HOTEL 
☀️ FREE FLIGHTS TO NYC
☀️ $500 FOR WHATEVER YOU’LL GET INTO 

Because we all deserve more summer. And more wine. TAG YOUR BESTIE WITH #SWEEPSTAKES TO ENTER.

BABE 100 MORE HOURS OF SUMMER GOV BALL GETAWAY SWEEPS. No Purchase Necessary. Open to US residents 21+. Must be a registered user and follow @drinkbabe on Instagram. Ends 9/7/21. See Official Rules at https://drinkbabe.net/pages/babe-100-more-hours-of-summer-gov-ball-getaway-sweeps-official-rules for prizes & details. Msg & data rates may apply. Void where prohibited.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by BABE on August 14, 2021. May be an image of drink and outdoors.

node.text: IF YOUR POOL DAY DOESN’T LOOK EXACTLY LIKE THIS, YOU’RE DOING IT WRONG. FIND THE BABE 100 VARIETY PACK IN STORES NATIONWIDE NOW. BECAUSE THE SUMMER WE DESERVE DESERVES EVEN MORE WINE. LINK IN BIO 😘

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by BABE on August 12, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Stepping outside like'.

node.text:
WE TEAMED UP WITH @RITDYE AND @MINNIDIP FOR THE SUMMER TIE-DYE GIVEAWAY YOU DESERVE:
✨@MINNIDIP $100 GIFT CARD + INFLATABLE POOL
✨@RITDYE SUMMER COLLECTION OF DYE + TIE-DYE ACCESSORY KIT
✨ $100 CREDIT TO @DRINKBABE + AMAZE BABE GEAR 
TO ENTER: FOLLOW US AT @DRINKBABE, AS WELL AS @MINNIDIP AND @RITDYE. THEN, TAG TWO FRIENDS 21+ USING #SWEEPSTAKES IN THE COMMENTS! WE WILL CHOOSE THREE LUCKY WINNERS.  YOU HAVE UNTIL 8/12 AT MIDNIGHT, SO WHAT ARE YOU WAITING FOR?

node.text: The transformational powers of coffee on ice cannot be overstated.
